{"tid":91920,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地細個比老豆老母打會唔會還拖？","createTime":"2017-01-23T07:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T05:46:19.000Z","uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dab98a81d8df8a4d172651a898fb6ef308dd558","tid":91920,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"細個比老豆打會還拖，不過唔夠打<br />\n大個少少夠佢打佢就唔敢打我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edf154230519e00dbe5dfaebf3d75e5cbdf6c14","tid":91920,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"諗起細個比人咁樣&ldquo;教&ldquo;<br />\n都幾恐怖<br />\n唔識教仔既真係唔好生"},{"pid":"1511697ef49bb855d97e2076536f2fe65e328115","tid":91920,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"打得好金會忍唔住真係會還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bad58c7ac5d3cae409ad13d380bdc4137aee79","tid":91920,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起細個比人咁樣&ldquo;教&ldquo;<br />\n都幾恐怖<br />\n唔識教仔既真係唔好生</blockquote><br />\n通常好過分先會打，例如返學打傷同學偷錢果d<br />\n但我唔明點解一定要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c407de4e68124a1ee629723060055a83bdfeff","tid":91920,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打得好金會忍唔住真係會還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會用武器打"},{"pid":"631db1cd290cbeef68c4d6b7e5901bcb5a74fe22","tid":91920,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"還過一次<br />\n打親通常有武器"},{"pid":"cc7254c6a03d70e858b55a735f5c752d9563029a","tid":91920,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗起細個比人咁樣&ldquo;教&ldquo;<br />\n都幾恐怖<br />\n唔識教仔既真係唔好生</blockquote><br />\n通常好過分先會打，例如返學打傷同學偷錢果d<br />\n但我唔明點解一定要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我周不時都要比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99600bd677321cc6400ba03e418307c3f32bfb6","tid":91920,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:15:26.000Z","msg":"由8歲打到14，5歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞晒武器咁打 又鐵通 實木劍 仲有好多 唔記得咗<br />\n大咗佢同我傾計 <br />\n話打者愛也<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我地感情好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a388c1b6093fcd95fd450fa083f98d482a7b35","tid":91920,"uid":78001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"今晚打老母"},{"pid":"65414274fec2b0f10ce96637645b6982d90e099a","tid":91920,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"我細過試過輕輕力還手打老母<br />\n其實都唔算打我都係輕輕力咁拍返佢<br />\n點解佢大大力一拳一拳咁打返我<br />\n我老豆係旁邊見到又食花生睇戲<br />\n見我地打起上黎又冇勸交又冇勸打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638103f50e58416fc081bc2d3770edfd98ee9c8c","tid":91920,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"試過有一次嬲得濟拎個風筒打返落老豆個頭到, 之後老豆話唔敢再打我<br />\n<br />\n依件事之後變成老母嘅花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31a3da331efc06d258e5171998b57b872d64611","tid":91920,"uid":71609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"試過還拖，點知比人打得仲金，以後唔敢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6a1b893993342e2d08ea2a844da14d5b76f562","tid":91920,"uid":25312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:46:19.000Z","msg":"唔會 不過有次打親條腰我差啲報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申嗰次行路會痛痛地"}]}